Package uniandes.communication

In this package are located all classes required to offer agent communication services in project.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMessageReceiver
    Class used to receive UDP messages and put the in threads to be executed
    MessageSender
    Class to send message to list of machines.
    PmMessageReceiver
    Receives message as reports about physical machines states and put it in message processor to be executed in thread pool
    VmMessageReceiver
    Receive message as reports about virtual machines states and put it in message processor to be executed in thread pool
